WEBVTT

00:05:27.040 --> 00:05:30.320
who are an amazing media collective
called Coletivo Papo Reto.

00:05:32.280 --> 00:05:35.120
Brazil is a tough place for human rights.

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:39.640
The Brazilian police
kills thousands of people every year.

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:42.720
The only time that
there's an investigation,

00:05:43.920 --> 00:05:45.120
guess when?

00:05:45.440 --> 00:05:46.640
When there's video.

00:05:48.240 --> 00:05:51.680
Seventeen-year-old Eduardo
was killed in broad daylight

00:05:52.640 --> 00:05:54.216
by the Rio police,

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.520
and look what happens after they kill him.

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:00.320
They put a gun in the dead boy's hand,